coupon.additional_terms:
港幣$50現金券
．此電子現金券適用於愛視美眼鏡鑽石山分店;
．使用此電子現金券時，請出示電子現金券作證明;
．此電子現金券逾期無效並不作補發及不設退款;
．此電子現金券適用於購買鏡架、鏡片、鏡架連鏡片、太陽眼鏡、隱形眼鏡;
．此電子現金券不適用購買特價品、眼科視光檢查、隱形眼鏡護理藥水、眼藥水和配件；
．使用此電子現金券之消費交易金額不可低於電子現金券之金額;
．每項交易只可使用 1 張 $50 電子現金券;
．每張電子現金券只可使用一次，不可累積使用;
．此電子現金券不得兌換現金;
．交易完成後，即代表已成功使用電子現金券;
．愛視美眼鏡保留修改以上優惠及細則之權利;
．如有任何爭議, 愛視美眼鏡將保留最終決定權;
．此電子現金券有效日期至 2024 年 12 月 31 日。

．The digital cash coupon is only suitable to Eye’s Mate Optical Diamond Hill branch;
．Please present the digital cash coupon as proof when using the coupon;
．The coupon is suitable for purchasing frames, lenses, frames with lenses, sunglasses, and contact lenses;
．The coupon is not suitable for purchasing eye examination fee, optical accessories, eye health solution;
．The coupon will be invalid and will not be reissued or refunded if the coupon is expired;
．The amount of consumption transactions using the coupon cannot be less than the amount of the coupon;
．Each transaction can only accept one digital coupon;
．Each coupon can only be used once and cannot be used cumulatively;
．The coupon cannot be exchanged for cash;
．The coupon will be nullified once the sales transaction is completed;
．Eye’s Mate Optical reserves the right to alter or terminate the coupon and amend the terms and conditions at any time without notice;
．In case of any dispute, Eye’s Mate Optical reserves the right to make the final decision;
．The coupon is valid for 31 Dec 2024.

